column3: The Cosmic Exploration Initiative has officially completed its operations on Sinus Ardorum!<hex:02100103><hex:02100103>Thanks to the hard work and diligence of contributors like you, we are ready to leap from our Lunar Hopopolis to frontiers unknown. 'Tis a dream come true!<hex:02100103><hex:02100103>We hope you will join us as we continue to seek delightful new discoveries on distant stars.<hex:02100103><hex:02100103>Sincerely,<hex:02100103>The Loporrits
